            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has softened, add your <strong>meat-free mince</strong>, <strong>ground cumin</strong>, <strong>smoked paprika</strong> and <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) to the pan and cook for 4-6 min or until browned, breaking it up with a wooden spoon as you go</p><p>Meanwhile, grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1618223253301-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1618223253301-x400.jpg",
