            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Increase the heat to high, add the <strong>tomato stock</strong> and cook for 3-4 min further or until the sauce has thickened to a ragù-like consistency – this is your <strong>smoky meat-free mince filling</strong></p><p>Grease an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong> with a little<strong> olive oil</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1618223290462-x200.jpg",
